resqtimeWorkflow.StepProgress1: Downloading the newest Loozend version. If download does not immediately start, click here
resqtimeWorkflow.StepProgress2: Double click on the downloaded file Loozendinstaller.exe. The installer will ask you to submit your e-mail address and password to check your identity.
resqtimeWorkflow.StepProgress3: Loozend will undertake an initial exploration of your disk. You may continue working regularly. This process may last between 6 hours and 2 days, depending on the amount of information stored in your disk and the available bandwidth. If you leave your computer turned on during the night, the process will be quicker.
